(1, 10, '1632431735prince2-t-peoplecert.gif', 'What is PRINCE2?', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#444444\"><b>PRINCE2</b> (Projects IN\r\nControlled Environments) is a project management method which is structured and\r\nit is a practitioner certification program. <b>PRINCE2</b> emphasizes dividing\r\nprojects into manageable and controllable stages.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#444444\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#444444\">It is adopted in many\r\ncountries throughout the world, including the UK, Western European countries,\r\nand Australia.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '1632431735Seven-principles-of-PRINCE2-methodology.png', 'ZdnTmpJP3BA', NULL, '<h1 style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><b style=\"\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">Learning</font></b></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#444444\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#444444\">Apply the proven PRINCE2 project management process model<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#444444\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#444444\">Implement the PRINCE2 principles, a framework of good practice<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#444444\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#444444\">Initiate projects with clear scope, agreed responsibilities, and\r\nacceptable risk levels<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#444444\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#444444\">Apply minimum controls to keep projects on track and deliver\r\nagreed levels of quality<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#444444\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">Benefits</font><font color=\"#444444\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0in;\">\r\n </ol><p style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">It gives stakeholder a chance\r\n     to have a say when it comes to decision making<o:p></o:p></span></p><ol style=\"margin-top: 0in;\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">This is the consistent approach<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">It focuses on business\r\n     justification<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">It provides the greater control\r\n     on the plan by regular reviews of project progress<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#444444\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">Why You Need PRINCE2</font><font color=\"#444444\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#444444\">PRINCE2 provides&nbsp;benefits to the managers and directors of a\r\nproject&nbsp;and to an organization, through the controllable use of\r\nresources and the ability to manage business and project risk more effectively.\r\nPRINCE2 embodies established and proven best practice in project management.<a name=\"_GoBack\"></a><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2021-09-24 02:15:35', '2021-09-24 02:15:35'),
(2, 12, '1632655490123.png', 'Course Description', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><b>ITIL</b> is the world’s leading best practice framework\r\nfor implementing IT Service Management. IT Service Management is introduced\r\nwith ITIL 4 through the lens of a Service Value System (SVS), which provides a\r\nholistic end-to-end view of how to successfully contribute to business value,\r\nand also how to leverage concepts from models such as Lean IT, Agile, DevOps\r\nand Organizational Change Management. This foundational course immerses a\r\nprofessional in the guiding principles, dimensions, and practices of <b>ITIL 4.</b><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '1632655490sifat.jpg', '5VanIRdzcrY', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><a name=\"_GoBack\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><b style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\"><font color=\"#ce0000\">Learning</font></span></b></span></a></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Use the ITIL terminology<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Identify the sub-activities for each best practice\r\nprocess<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Understand your role and responsibilities regarding\r\nIT Service Management<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Understand aspects of implementing ITIL processes\r\nand creating a cycle of continuous improvement<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><font color=\"#ce0000\">Benefits</font><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Faster and more\r\nflexible service delivery practices to support digital transformation<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·