(32, 40, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">The <b>ISO/IEC 27001 Lead Auditor</b> certification consists\r\nof professional certification for auditors who are specialized in information\r\nsecurity management systems (ISMS) based on the ISO/IEC 27001 standard.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">The training of lead auditors generally includes a\r\nclassroom/online training and exam portion and a requirement to have performed\r\na number of ISO/IEC 27001 audits and a number of years of information security\r\nexperience. Some <b>ISO 27001 Lead Audito</b>r training courses are formally accredited\r\nby training accreditation bodies such as IRCA and <b>PECB</b>. Attending the course\r\nand passing the exam is not sufficient for an individual to use the credentials\r\nof Lead Auditor as professional and audit experience is required. The specific\r\nrequirements to obtain a certificate stating the qualification of\r\n\"<b>ISO27001 Lead Auditor</b>\" vary depending on the organization issuing\r\nthe certificate.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '•	Avoid hefty fines. ISO 27001 is the accepted global benchmark for the effective management of information assets.\r\n•	Protect your reputation.\r\n•	Comply with business, legal, contractual and regulatory requirements.\r\n•	Improve structure and focus. \r\n•	Reduce the need for frequent audits.', '<ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\n     tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n     11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Understand a\r\n     Privacy Information Management System (PIMS) and its processes based on\r\n     ISO/IEC 27701<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\n     tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n     11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Identify the\r\n     relationship between ISO/IEC 27701, ISO/IEC 27001, ISO/IEC 27002, and\r\n     other standards and regulatory frameworks<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\n     tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n     11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Acquire the\r\n     competencies of the auditor’s role in planning, leading, and following up\r\n     on a management system audit in accordance with ISO 19011.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\n     tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n     11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Learn how to\r\n     interpret the requirements of ISO/IEC 27701 in the context of a PIMS audit<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Prerequisites<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">A fundamental understanding of information security\r\nand privacy, and comprehensive knowledge of audit principles.</span></p>', '1633950389PECB 1000,6000.jpg', 7, 30, 40, 40, 'Multiple Choice Questions', 90, 'Closed', '2021-10-11 03:06:29', '2021-10-11 03:06:29'),
(33, 41, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">This is a foundation-level course designed to provide you with an&nbsp;understanding<b> of </b>Big Data, the potential sources of Big\r\nData that can be used for solving real business problems and also provide an\r\noverview of Data Mining and the tools used in it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">The <b>Big Data Foundations</b>\r\ncourse provides you with an understanding of big data, potential data sources\r\nthat can be used for solving real business problems, and an overview of data mining\r\nand the tools used in it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">This is a fundamentals\r\ncourse with practical exercises designed to provide you with hands-on\r\nexperience in using two of the most popular technologies in big data processing\r\n– Hadoop and MongoDB.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'This certification provides an understanding of Big Data, potential data sources that can be used to solve real-world problems, and an overview of data mining and its capabilities. Certification will help you become a Big Data Ready Professional.', '<ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"square\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\n     font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Explain Big Data, its origin, and its\r\n     characteristics.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\n     font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Discuss the tools applicable to Big\r\n     Data processing.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\n     font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Explain data mining.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\n     font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Discuss the popular Big Data\r\n     technologies – Hadoop and MongoDB.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\n     font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Discuss the Big Data projects and the\r\n     main players involved.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\n     font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Identify and obtain relevant datasets\r\n     when looking at a business problem.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\n     font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Install and manage Big Data\r\n     processing environments based on Hadoop or MongoDB at a departmental\r\n     level.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>', '1634017335big data foundation.psd1000 6000.jpg', 8, 28, 40, 40, 'Multiple Choice Questions', 60, 'Closed', '2021-10-11 21:42:15', '2021-10-11 21:42:15'),
(34, 42, '<div>The course will cover the eight key areas of the<b> COBIT 2019</b> including: framework introduction, principles, governance system and components, governance and management objectives, performance management, designing a tailored governance system, business case and implementation.</div><div><br></div>', '<div><b>COBIT®</b> is a framework for the enterprise governance and management of information and technology (I&amp;T) that supports enterprise goal achievement.</div><div>The<b> COBIT 2019 Foundation</b> course is intended for current COBIT 5 certificate holders as well as those new to COBIT who are interested in achieving the latest foundation certificate.</div><div>In this course, delegates will be taught about the concepts, models and key definitions of COBIT framework and helps prepare learners to take the <b>COBIT 2019 Foundation </b>exam.</div><div><br></div>', 'Intended for more experienced COBIT users, the certificate program supports enterprise goal achievement. The COBIT 2019 Design and Implementation Certificate affirms holder’s ability to understand, design and implement programs for the enterprise governance of IT (EGIT).', '<div>New framework introduction</div><div>Key concepts and terminology</div><div>Governance and Framework Principles</div><div>Governance system and components</div><div>Governance and management objectives</div><div>Performance management</div><div>Designing a tailored governance system</div><div><br></div>', '1634018157Itil4 foundation1000. 600psd.jpg', 9, 49, 75, 75, 'Multiple Choice Questions', 120, 'Closed', '2021-10-11 21:55:57', '2021-10-11 21:55:57'),
(35, 43, '<b>Project Management Professional (PMP)</b> certification is an industry recognized credential for project managers. PMP demonstrates the experience, education, skill and competency required to lead and direct projects', '<div><b>Project Management Professional (PMP)</b> is the designation awarded by the Project Management Institute to project management professionals who fulfil certain education and experience criteria. It is a certificate of their superior project management knowledge and skill.</div><div>The PMP certification is globally recognized and is very beneficial to project management professionals in many ways. Since the certification acts as an assurance of the professionals’ quality and skill, it has a direct impact on the earning capacity of professionals receiving it.</div>', 'The PMP, also known as project management professional certification, is unbiased proof of a person\'s project management talents and expertise. It is accepted worldwide and gives better career opportunities, credibility, and increased income for those who have acquired it.', '<div>Increased salary.</div><div>Understanding project management methodologies.</div><div>Global acknowledgement.</div><div>More job opportunities.</div><div>Better job performance.</div><div>Applicable to any industry.</div><div>Security during economic downturns and recessions.</div><div>Become part of a global community.</div><div><br></div>', '1634018942pmp1000 600 psd.jpg', 10, 141, 175, 175, 'Multiple Choice Questions', 230, 'Closed', '2021-10-11 22:09:02', '2021-10-11 22:09:02');
INSERT INTO `classroom_infos` (`id`, `classroom_course_id`, `classroom_short_description`, `classroom_course_description`, `classroom_certification`, `classroom_learning_outcomes`, `classroom_banner_image`, `classroom_instructor_id`, `pass_mark`, `out_of`, `no_of_questions`, `exam_type`, `duration`, `book`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(36, 44, '<div><b>CISA </b>is an abbreviated form of <b>Certified Information Systems Auditor.</b> CISA certificate is suitable for individuals who have a have an interest in information systems auditing, control, and security. <b>CISA </b>is a professional certification which is provided by the ISACA.</div><div><br></div>', '<div>The <b>Certified Information Systems Auditor (CISA)</b> is a certification and a globally recognized standard for appraising an IT auditor\'s knowledge, expertise and skill in assessing vulnerabilities and instituting IT controls in an enterprise environment.</div><div>An ISACA Certified Information Systems Auditor is recognized as one of the leading authorities in the areas of IS auditing, control, and information security. This official <b>CISA </b>training course provides you with in-depth coverage of the five<b> CISA</b> domains that are covered on the<b> CISA</b> certification exam. These domains include auditing information systems; IT governance and management of IT; information systems acquisition, development, and implementation; information systems operations, maintenance, and support; and protection of information assets</div>', 'If you are an entry-level to mid-career professional, CISA can showcase your expertise and assert your ability to apply a risk-based approach to planning, executing and reporting on audit engagements. Gain instant credibility in your interactions with internal stakeholders, regulators, external auditors, and customers.', '<div>Prepare for and pass the Certified Information Systems Auditor (CISA) Exam</div><div><br></div><div>Develop and implement a risk-based IT audit strategy in compliance with IT audit standards</div><div><br></div><div>Evaluate the effectiveness of an IT governance structure</div><div><br></div><div>Ensure that the IT organizational structure and human resources (personnel) management support the organization’s strategies and objectives</div><div><br></div><div>Review the information