(14, 43, 'uploads/trainer/1715672859753318.png', 'uploads/trainer/1715672859753340.png', 'Mohammad Samsuddin Rana', 'Lead Project Management Consultant', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/samsuddin-rana-cssbb-pmp-rmp-prince2-cisa-scjp-mcp-92717466/', '<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:\r\nAR-SA\">Mohammad Samsuddin Rana, with over 10,000 hours of project delivery\r\nexperience, is one of the project and change management expert in Bangladesh.\r\nHe has more than 15 years extensive experience in audit, quality, project and\r\nstrategy management for different industries in Bangladesh. Currently he is the\r\nHead of Software Development at United Finance (a Foreign investment\r\norganization) and working on Core Banking System (CBS).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAs a trainer he started his journey with PMP exam preparation course. He\r\nconducted various training programs among which many successful training\r\nprograms were unique in nature.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHe has achieved the RMP &amp; PMP credential from PMI (Project Management\r\nInstitute), USA, CISA certification from ISACA (Information Systems Audit and\r\nControl Association), USA, PRINCE2(P) certification from AXELOS, United\r\nKingdom, Sun Certified Java Programmer (SCJP) from Sun Microsystems, USA &amp;\r\nMicrosoft Certified Professional from Microsoft, USA.</span>', '2021-11-06 02:05:42', NULL),
