(4, 11, '16339451541632983199Blockchain Explained inner banner.png', '<div><b><font color=\"#ce0000\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;;\">8th October, 2021</span><br></font></b></div><div><b><font color=\"#ce0000\"><br></font></b></div><div><b><font color=\"#ce0000\">6 PM – 9 PM</font></b></div>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;;\">﻿</span><font face=\"Arial Black\">Blockchain is a hot topic within the industry at present as more and more organizations are using the technology to process cryptocurrency payments between different parties.&nbsp;</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\"><br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\">This course has been designed to explain what the technology is and how it works at a high level. You will build an awareness of Blockchain technology and how it can be used to process cryptocurrency transactions across an open and distributed ledger.&nbsp;</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\"><br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\">By the end of this course, you will also be able to determine how Blockchain can support your business operations.</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\"><br></font></p><p><font color=\"#ce0000\"><b><font face=\"Arial Black\">&nbsp;</font><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;;\">Benefits</span></b></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\">·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Huge demand for blockchain professionals</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\"><br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\">·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Huge salary</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\"><br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\">·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Better exposure to latest tech</font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\"><br></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial Black\">·&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Edge over others</font></p>', '2021-10-11 01:39:14', '2021-10-11 01:39:14'),
